#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the <button>Edit</button> button</h2>
<button>Edit</button> open the record for modification.  Fields that can be modified will
be display as html input widgets (input texts, textareas, selects etc).  Fields that cannot
be modified will simply be printed.
<p>
<u><b>Important</b></u>:  You must hit the <button>Update</button> to save your work.

